descript.supplinf: This dataset has been adjusted to the NAD83(NSRS2007) coordinates. ESRI does not support this new datum explicitly, so the datum associated with the dataset is listed as NAD83(HARN). The dataset has been adjusted from NAD83(HARN) by shifting the coordinates by .24 US feet north and .23 US feet east using the Project tool with a false easting and northing. This amounts to a 3.99 inch shift to the northeast. To match this dataset to NAD83(HARN) datasets, adjust the coordinates of this dataset by .24 US feet south and .23 US feet west.
